{"tid":478755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔報復？】「中朝友誼橋」突關閉 中國外交部：北韓稱維修","createTime":"2017-11-24T11:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T13:35:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c77c0052bb69acf931d647495c870f5b379a018","tid":478755,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171124/large/1511521883_32b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171124%2Flarge%2F1511521883_32b0.jpg&h=e3388f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n習總特使宋濤上周訪問北韓，盛傳未能與北韓領導人金正恩會面後，引起中方不滿，中國國航突宣佈無限期停飛北京至平壤的航線，中朝關係緊張升級。據日本媒體報道，位於丹東市、連接中國與北韓的中朝友誼橋今日突然關閉，傳關閉10天。中國外交部發言人耿爽今日在例行記者會上證實，接壤中國丹東地區及北韓的中朝友誼橋，因朝方提出橋面維修，於近日臨時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說：「據我了解，近期，因朝方需對橋面進行維修，中朝友誼橋將臨時關閉，待維修工作結束後該橋將恢復正常通行。」記者問他中朝友誼橋是何時關閉的？將關閉多長時間？耿爽只答：「據我了解，是近期將臨時關閉」。<br />\n<br />\n據日媒報道，中朝友誼橋暫時關閉10天，由今日至下月3日。<br />\n<br />\n中朝友誼橋對上一次關閉，是於2015年9月28日，當時因為橋面破損和一輛卡車傾覆而被封閉，30日臨時通行一天後又封橋，至2015年11月2日重新通車。<br />\n<br />\n讀賣新聞／海外網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171124/57500325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F57500325&d=P7RVNT%2BZnjVYvEPP2GZcp%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=58b71ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F57500325&h=c9d14601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171124/57500325</a>"},{"pid":"30b906835525106fe98620a01ae91a5b0f516601","tid":478755,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T23:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d134b20981ce8b268cc9ab244006446d7525c56","tid":478755,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4322c56e609fb8ed586751c5b8173d6f46facd8f","tid":478755,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}